summary: updated Army of one in 2017 to make it a little better
descriptionHtml: after a break from skyrim modding I came back to put up the new Army Of One mod this version has no moaning and instead of one npc summoning one npc this version has one npc summoning four npc's, one knight and three archers. In this version I also made a summon spell for the player so they can have a summoned version, it's on the shadow knight himself just trade and take it.....enjoy :)
author: Ghhost
